commitResults.messageBody:
This commit cleans up `JsonAdaptedPersonTest.java` to resolve the style
violations introduced during the integration of the mandatory `Status`
field.

The primary issues addressed were:

1.  **Line Length:** Long constructor calls in test methods were
reformatted into multi-line calls to adhere to the 120-character limit.
2.  **Wildcard Imports:** Replaced the use of
`import seedu.address.model.person.*` with specific, individual class
imports to maintain code clarity.

No functional logic related to parsing or model validation was changed
in this commit; it is purely a stylistic cleanup to allow the CI
pipeline to pass Checkstyle.
